# @no-log
# CoreGearERP M2 End-to-End Flow Test
# Tests the complete goods receipt flow from product creation to stock movement
# Run against a clean database or a dedicated test tenant

### Step 0 -- Reset test data
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/test/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

> {%
    client.test("Test data cleared", function() {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "Expected 200");
    });
%}

